# Staubli UK Ltd

> UK subsidiary of Stäubli International AG, supplying precision connectors, robotic systems and quick-release coupling solutions to aerospace and defence markets.

## What they do

Stäubli develops and manufactures quick-release couplings for hydraulics, pneumatics, fuels and electrical power and data, alongside robotic tool changers and multi-coupling systems. The group serves aerospace and defence customers across 29 countries, with the UK entity based in Telford.

## Products and solutions

- **Quick-release couplings** - Hydraulic, pneumatic and fuel couplings for demanding aerospace and defence platforms.
- **Robotic tool changers** - Automated end-of-arm tooling solutions for manufacturing and integration workflows.
- **Electrical connectors** - Power, signal and data connectors for platform and system integration.

